title: GOP Congressman Booed At Tea Party

content: Rep. Gresham Barrett -- the upstate congressman running for South Carolina governor next year -- got a frosty response at the Tea Party in conservative Greenville Friday for his support of the bailout last year. They made a statement that is why I like about it. Whether or not all booed is irrelevent, the majority made a statement. Rep or Dem. That's 1 tea party I would have went too. Americans need to break free from the political bonds and make that same statement.
